/span>，傳送一隻就會有超極巨美錄梅塔。<br />\n<br />\nSWITCH連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.nintendo.com/JP/ja/titles/70010000016930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.nintendo.com%2FJP%2Fja%2Ftitles%2F70010000016930&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=e9ad1658\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.nintendo.com/JP/ja/titles/70010000016930</a><br />\nAN連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.pokemon.pokemonhome\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.pokemon.pokemonhome&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=b1f04142\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.pokemon.pokemonhome</a><br />\niOS連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/id1485352913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1485352913&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=7a4d2279\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/id1485352913</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGyHxVR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGyHxVR.png&h=586ef74f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"115aa8663e7c450ee0863b119ff0f2e4b311e453","tid":2479040,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">Pokemon 最新消息</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">《Pokemon 晶燦鑽石》</span><br />\n<span class=\"violet\">《Pokemon 明亮珍珠》</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NA1Nj53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNA1Nj53.jpg&h=1d1453bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重現「神奧地區」的冒險<br />\n《Pokemon 晶燦鑽石》《Pokemon 明亮珍珠》的冒險舞台位於「神奧地區」。在這片綠意盎然的大地上，巍峨的天冠山聳立於中央，而且有諸多神話流傳下來。主角將探訪「神奧地區」內的各個地方，以成為小精靈聯盟的冠軍為目標 <br />\n<br />\n城鎮和道路等場地細膩地以《Pokemon 鑽石／珍珠》的尺寸重現。曾經遊玩過原作的人，能帶著回憶再次踏上熟悉的地方，重溫那段冒險之旅；初次來到神奧地區冒險的人，也將在這段旅途上遇到許許多多的邂逅和驚奇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8LFE6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8LFE6b.png&h=db1681d0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbkBXST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbkBXST.jpg&h=49f4f5e4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbErAEH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbErAEH.png&h=921d9213&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0TLRcY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0TLRcY.png&h=7a67e57a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">《Pokemon 傳說 阿爾宙斯》</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpojVFP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpojVFP.jpg&h=8e491341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n融合了「動作」與「RPG」，挑戰Pokemon系列全新表現方式的作品。本作將以神奧地區為舞台，描述與Pokemon DP距離久遠的過去時代。主角的目標是製作出這個地區的第一本Pokemon圖鑑。透過鍥而不捨地捕捉、調查、研究棲息在這片土地上的Pokemon，朝著完成Pokemon圖鑑這個目標邁進。<br />\n<br />\n在遊戲世界中縱橫馳騁，捕捉許多Pokemon並且逐步完成圖鑑。這些Pokemon系列特有的遊戲樂趣將會在本作中以嶄新的角度來呈現，令玩家更貼近感受由Pokemon與人物角色所打造出的世界。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>起手御三家 (蕭巴成為最大贏家)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5fN4zD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5fN4zD.jpg&h=d29be4c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>主角</strong><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ge6Q2mk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGe6Q2mk.jpg&h=6c9999bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>結合開放式世界冒險元素與經典回合制遊戲</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTvyfGJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTvyfGJ.jpg&h=b5b9d9c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvB5Re3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvB5Re3.jpg&h=d3e6a3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>真主角</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXqay3sDH7VTNfEW9UU7U3tBsT5eikkxPShKso8PDyFYX?filename=nSKSwfi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnSKSwfi.jpg&h=f25d404a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ed471644853b71ad1b3898ba58ddf41ff641f14","tid":2479040,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04d464f81313c31841dad16cff54e5f37de31a0","tid":2479040,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed471644853b71ad1b3898ba58ddf41ff641f14","tid":2479040,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b998386b719d4b40ca7b6f7cfe08669e99b686","tid":2479040,"uid":71429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:52:04.000Z","msg":"Where is PC集會所？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4471fb2152c6ec23a225165b62355a2d133d1097","tid":2479040,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:25:59.000Z",